title: Wayne Wildrick from Man Overboard
itunes:title: Wayne Wildrick from Man Overboard
description:
Wayne Wildrick, the guitarist of Man Overboard, dropped by my house recently to go over his upbringing in New Jersey, what he was thinking when he left the band for a brief time and we invent the term, "drinking the paper".
